## Build a REST API using Spring Boot with the help of GitHub Copilot

# Download the software packages
https://aka.ms/download-jdk/microsoft-jdk-17.0.12-windows-x64.msi
https://downloads.apache.org/maven/maven-3/3.9.11/binaries/apache-maven-3.9.11-bin.zip

# Install microsoft JDK
# Install apache- maven > Extract All > Setup Environmental variables 
# Click New under User variable for Admin section.
# Variable name:JAVA_HOME
# Variable value:C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.8.0_271
# select Path and click Edit under User variable for Admin section > New
# %JAVA_HOME%\bin

# set up the environment and path variables for Maven.
# select New under User variable for Admin section
# Variable name: MAVEN_HOME
# Variable value: C:\Users\Admin\Downloads\apache-maven-3.9.11
# select Path and click Edit > New
# %MAVEN_HOME%\bin

